metadata.title: Serve Clean Smart Toothpick Dispenser, White
features: Serve Clean Smart Toothpick Dispenser delivers single unwrapped toothpicks without germ transfer.
Works with USB cord (USB cord included) or 4 AA batteries. (Batteries not included)
Includes handy "Touch Free" tong for easy loading from toothpick carton to dispenser.
Dual bulbs direct UV light directly into the storage compartment during every cycle.
Includes Serve Clean brand white birch toothpicks starter pack.
description: The Serve Clean Smart Toothpick dispenser provides a unique patented method of delivering cost saving unwrapped toothpicks from machine to user without touching anything but the toothpick. With the simple wave of your hand, one round wood toothpick rises from the UV filled storage compartment directly to you. Includes handy "Touch Free" tong for easy loading from toothpick carton to dispenser.
